---
import PitchSlide from "../PitchSlide.astro";
---

<PitchSlide
	id="market"
	title="Market Opportunity"
	subtitle="Tapping into massive, growing trends"
	bgColor="var(--bg-secondary)"
>
	<div class="market-content">
		<div class="market-trends mb-5">
			<h3>Global Market Size & Growth</h3>
			<div class="trends-grid grid grid-2">
				<div class="trend-card card">
					<h4>Global Meal Kit Market</h4>
					<p>
						The global meal kit delivery market was valued at USD 20.54 billion in 2022 
						and is projected to grow at 15.3% CAGR through 2030, reaching USD 64.27 billion<sup>1</sup>.
					</p>
					<div class="trend-stat">
						<span class="stat-number">15.3%</span>
						<span class="stat-label">Global CAGR 2023-2030</span>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="trend-card card">
					<h4>MENA Market Opportunity</h4>
					<p>
						The Middle East meal kit market is USD 432M (2024) growing at 15.7% CAGR<sup>2</sup>, 
						while GCC food e-commerce represents USD 4.2B with 19% CAGR<sup>3</sup>.
					</p>
					<div class="trend-stat">
						<span class="stat-number">19%</span>
						<span class="stat-label">GCC Food E-commerce CAGR</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="market-trends mb-5">
			<h3>Content-Driven Food Discovery</h3>
			<div class="trends-grid grid grid-2">
				<div class="trend-card card">
					<h4>Social Media Recipe Discovery</h4>
					<p>
						68% of consumers discover new recipes through social media platforms<sup>4</sup>, 
						with Middle East Instagram penetration at 74% of internet users<sup>5</sup>.
					</p>
					<div class="trend-stat">
						<span class="stat-number">68%</span>
						<span class="stat-label">discover recipes via social media</span>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="trend-card card">
					<h4>Growing Home Cooking Trend</h4>
					<p>
						54% of consumers cook more at home than before<sup>6</sup>, with 22% ordering 
						meal kits more frequently as they seek convenience without sacrificing quality.
					</p>
					<div class="trend-stat">
						<span class="stat-number">22%</span>
						<span class="stat-label">increased meal kit ordering</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="market-expansion">
			<h3>Our Regional Strategy</h3>
			<div class="expansion-map">
				<div class="expansion-phase">
					<span class="phase-number">1</span>
					<div class="phase-content">
						<h4>Dubai & UAE Launch</h4>
						<p>
							Target market with avg. delivery basket of AED 95 ($26)<sup>7</sup> 
							and strong digital food adoption
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="expansion-phase">
					<span class="phase-number">2</span>
					<div class="phase-content">
						<h4>GCC Region Expansion</h4>
						<p>
							Scale to Saudi Arabia, Qatar, Kuwait leveraging similar 
							demographics and food culture preferences
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="expansion-phase">
					<span class="phase-number">3</span>
					<div class="phase-content">
						<h4>MENA Hub Development</h4>
					<p>
						Expand content-commerce model to Egypt, Jordan, Lebanon 
						with localized cuisine and creator partnerships
					</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="references">
			<h4>Sources</h4>
			<ol class="text-sm">
				<li>Grand View Research, "Meal Kit Delivery Services Market Report" (2023)</li>
				<li>Grand View Research, Middle East Market Analysis (2024)</li>
				<li>Statista Digital Market Insights, GCC Food E-commerce (2023)</li>
				<li>Hootsuite "Digital 2024" Global Overview Report</li>
				<li>DataReportal "Digital 2024" Middle East Report (Jan 2024)</li>
				<li>HUNTER Consumer Survey (2020), cited in Grand View Research</li>
				<li>Talabat Annual Report (2023)</li>
			</ol>
		</div>
	</div>
</PitchSlide>

<style>
	/* Market Section */
	.trend-stat {
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
		text-align: center;
		padding: 1rem;
		background-color: rgba(46, 196, 182, 0.1);
		border-radius: var(--radius-md);
	}

	.stat-number {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--color-secondary);
	}

	.expansion-map {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 2rem;
		margin-top: 2rem;
	}

	.expansion-phase {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1.5rem;
		align-items: center;
	}

	.phase-number {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		width: 3rem;
		height: 3rem;
		background-color: var(--color-primary);
		color: white;
		border-radius: 50%;
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}

	.mb-5 {
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}

	.references {
		margin-top: 3rem;
		padding-top: 2rem;
		border-top: 1px solid rgba(46, 196, 182, 0.2);
	}

	.references ol {
		margin-top: 1rem;
		padding-left: 1.5rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
		color: #666;
	}

	.references li {
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	sup {
		font-size: 0.7em;
		color: var(--color-secondary);
		font-weight: 600;
	}
</style> 